summary: AN ORDINANCE transferring jurisdiction of certain real property located within or adjacent to West Duwamish and East Duwamish Greenbelts and Cheasty, Longfellow Creek and Duwamish Head Greenspaces from the Executive Services Department to the Department of Parks and Recreation; and ratifying and confirming the acceptance of a deed for a portion of the foregoing real property located in West Duwamish Greenbelt.
